data.description:
Beautifully updated home in the quiet neighborhood of Westmoreland Heights. This home
features an open concept which is great for entertaining. The recent updates include luxury
vinyl flooring throughout the first floor, quartz counters in the kitchen and bathrooms, modern black faucets,  black and gold cabinet hardware, new
hexagon tile back splash, fresh paint, single bowl SS sink, SS cooktop and microwave, and 2”
blinds, new AC.  Upstairs has a game room with a wet bar. The fifth bedroom on the first floor could be
used as an office. The home sits on an oversized corn lot. This home is ready for its new owners
and to entertain family and friends!
